}{

{\ottdrulename{Jv\_snd}}{}%

\newcommand{\ottdruleJEXXvar}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\mathit{x}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t}  \mathrel{\in}  \Gamma}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash{}  \mathit{x}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t}}{%
{\ottdrulename{JE\_var}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleJEXXlam}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{x}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
\ottpremise{\mathit{x} \, \mathrel{\in!} \, \ottnt{E}}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash{}  \lambda{} \, \mathit{x}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \ottsym{.}  \ottnt{E}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \otimes{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}{%
{\ottdrulename{JE\_lam}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleJEXXapp}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \otimes{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}} \, \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}{%
{\ottdrulename{JE\_app}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleJEXXtt}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash{}  \mathop{ \textbf ! }  \colon{}  \textbf{I}}{%
{\ottdrulename{JE\_tt}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleJEXXstep}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \colon{}  \textbf{I}}%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t}}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \ottsym{;}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t}}{%
{\ottdrulename{JE\_step}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleJEXXfanout}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \ottsym{,}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \otimes{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}{%
{\ottdrulename{JE\_fanout}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleJEXXlet}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\mathit{x} \, \mathrel{\in!} \, \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
\ottpremise{\mathit{y} \, \mathrel{\in!} \, \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \otimes{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{x}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{y}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{3}}}}}%
}{
\Gamma  \vdash{}  \mathbin{\textbf{let} } \, \mathit{x}  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{y}  \ottsym{=}  \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{1}}}} \, \mathbin{\textbf{in} } \, \ottnt{E_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{3}}}}}{%
{\ottdrulename{JE\_let}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefnJE}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$\Gamma  \vdash{}  \ottnt{E}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t}$}{}

\newcommand{\ottdrulesatXXstep}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \sigma  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottnt{E} [  \mathop{ \textbf ! }  ] }%
\ottpremise{ \sigma'  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottnt{E'} [  \ottnt{N}  ] }%
}{
 \sigma  \cup{}  \sigma'  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottsym{(}  \ottnt{E}  \ottsym{;}  \ottnt{E'}  \ottsym{)} [  \ottnt{N}  ] }{%
{\ottdrulename{sat\_step}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulesatXXfanout}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\ottpremise{ \sigma'  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottnt{E'} [  \ottnt{N'}  ] }%
}{
 \sigma  \cup{}  \sigma'  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottsym{(}  \ottnt{E}  \ottsym{,}  \ottnt{E'}  \ottsym{)} [  \ottnt{N}  \ottsym{,}  \ottnt{N'}  ] }{%
{\ottdrulename{sat\_fanout}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulesatXXlet}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\ottpremise{ \sigma'  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{x}  \mathbin{:=}  \ottnt{N_{{\mathrm{0}}}}  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{y}  \mathbin{:=}  \ottnt{N_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottnt{E'} [  \ottnt{N_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  ] }%
}{
 \sigma  \cup{}  \sigma'  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottsym{(}  \mathbin{\textbf{let} } \, \mathit{x}  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{y}  \ottsym{=}  \ottnt{E} \, \mathbin{\textbf{in} } \, \ottnt{E'}  \ottsym{)} [  \ottnt{N_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  ] }{%
{\ottdrulename{sat\_let}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulesatXXlam}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \sigma  \ottsym{,}  \mathit{x}  \mathbin{:=}  \ottnt{N}  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottnt{E} [  \ottnt{N'}  ] }%
}{
 \sigma  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottsym{(}  \lambda{} \, \mathit{x}  \colon{}  \ottnt{t}  \ottsym{.}  \ottnt{E}  \ottsym{)} [  \ottnt{N}  \ottsym{,}  \ottnt{N'}  ] }{%
{\ottdrulename{sat\_lam}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulesatXXapp}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\ottpremise{ \sigma'  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottnt{E'} [  \ottnt{N}  ] }%
}{
 \sigma  \cup{}  \sigma'  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottsym{(}  \ottnt{E} \, \ottnt{E'}  \ottsym{)} [  \ottnt{N'}  ] }{%
{\ottdrulename{sat\_app}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefnsat}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$ \sigma  \mathrel{\vdash}  \ottnt{E} [  \ottnt{N}  ] $}{}
